title: Clear Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This restaurant is  decorated throughout in a modernist style. Offers juices, desserts, smoothies, salads, and mains. Vegetarian, vegan, and raw food clearly indicated. Directions: Located opposite the Bridges restaurant. The price range from US$12-20 for a 3-course meal, though one could also each a filling main dish for $5; moderate for foreigners but expensive by local standard. No alcohol. Previously located at Jalan Hanoman, Sep 2015.
